rit; vertical-align: baseline;\">19032 - System Analyst (Manajer) - DPSI</li><li style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">19033 - System Analyst (Asisten Manajer) - DPSI</li><li style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">19034 - Technology Architect (Manajer) - DPSI</li><li style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">19035 - Technology Architect (Asisten Manajer) - DPSI</li></ul><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">PERSYARATAN UMUM</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><ul style=\"margin: 0.5em 0em 0.5em 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4em; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: outside; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a href=\"http://www.bi.go.id/id/tentang-bi/bi-dan-publik/karir/Documents/Kualifikasi%20Tenaga%20Kerja%20PKWT%20Contact%20Center%20Bank%20Indonesia.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 127, 255); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.25s;\">​Kualifikasi Tenaga Kerja PKWT Contact Center Bank Indonesia</a></li><li style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a href=\"http://www.bi.go.id/id/tentang-bi/bi-dan-publik/karir/Documents/Kualifikasi%20Tenaga%20Kerja%20PKWT%20Information%20System%20Bank%20Indonesia%202017.pdf\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 127, 255); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.25s;\">​Kualifikasi Tenaga Kerja PKWT Information System Bank Indonesia</a></li></ul><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">PERSYARATAN LAINNYA</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><ol style=\"margin: 0.5em 0em 0.5em 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: outside; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Bersedia ditempatkan di Kantor Pusat Bank Indonesia dengan jangka waktu kontrak ± 2 tahun;</li><li style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Tidak sedang menjalani ikatan dinas atau bersedia melepaskan ikatan dinas dengan institusi lain apabila diterima di Bank Indonesia.</li><li style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Tidak memiliki saudara kandung/suami/istri yang sedang bekerja sebagai calon pegawai/pegawai/ pihak lain (outsourcing dan tenaga kerja PKWT) di Bank Indonesia;</li></ol><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">PEMBUKAAN LOWONGAN</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Senin 27 Februari 2017 (pukul 13.00 WIB) s.d Jumat 3 Maret 2017 (pukul 13.00 WIB)</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Bagi anda para pencari kerja yang tertarik untuk berkarir bersama Bank Indonesia dan memenuhi segala kebutuhan yang dipersyaratkan pada&nbsp;</span><b style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><a href=\"http://www.openkerja.com/2015/10/lowongan-kerja-bank-indonesia-bi.html\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 127, 255); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.25s;\">Lowongan Kerja Bank Indonesia Terbaru</a></b><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;bulan Maret 2017 diatas, maka silahkan siapkan berkas lamaran kerja lengkap seperti surat lamaran kerja, CV, foto terbaru serta dokumen pelengkap atau pendukung lainnya.</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Adapun tata cara yang telah ditetapkan dalam proses rekrutmen ini yaitu dengan melakukan pendaftaran dan penyampaian dokumen kelengkapan administrasi permohonan dilakukan dengan cara sebagai berikut:</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center;\"><b style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\"><a href=\"http://www.bi.go.id/id/tentang-bi/bi-dan-publik/karir/contents/Default.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 127, 255); text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; transition: all 0.25s;\">PENDAFTARAN</a></b></div><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">KETENTUAN PENGISIAN LAMARAN</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><ol style=\"margin: 0.5em 0em 0.5em 2em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-variant-numeric: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 16px; line-height: inherit; font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; vertical-align: baseline; list-style-position: outside; list-style-image: initial; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Pendaftaran hanya dapat dilakukan melalui http://www.bi.go.id/id/tentang-bi/bi-dan-publik/karir. Panitia seleksi tidak menerima lamaran melalui pos atau media pengiriman lainnya.</li><li style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Pilih bidang/posisi yang dilamar, misalnya: 19005 - Team Leader;</li><li style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Dalam pengisian form ini, tidak perlu menyampaikan attachment CV dan cukup mengisi data pribadi secara benar dan lengkap;</li><li style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Setiap lamaran hanya mengisi 1 (satu) lamaran untuk 1 (satu) lowongan pekerjaan. Pelamar yang mengisi lebih dari 1 (satu) lowongan pekerjaan akan otomatis terhapus dari sistem.</li><li style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Bagi pelamar yang pernah mengisi data diri pada form CV online, diwajibkan untuk memperbarui lamaran dengan mengisi form sesuai jabatan yang dibuka;</li><li style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Hasil tiap tahapan seleksi akan diumumkan melalui email kepada seluruh peserta;</li><li style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Seleksi akan dilaksanakan di kota Jakarta. Biaya transportasi dan akomodasi menjadi tanggungan peserta seleksi;</li><li style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Hanya kandidat terbaik (shortlisted candidates) dengan mempertimbangkan aspek-aspek keseluruhan yang akan diproses ke tahap selanjutnya;</li><li style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Tidak dipungut biaya apapun dalam proses seleksi calon pegawai Bank Indonesia. Mohon berhati-hati terhadap penipuan, apabila ada pihak yang berusaha meminta biaya/menjanjikan sesuatu/menawarkan bantuan atas proses rekrutmen dan seleksi dapat melapor kepada Contact Center BICARA.</li><li style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline;\">Keputusan hasil seleksi merupakan wewenang Bank Indonesia yang bersifat mutlak dan final.</li></ol><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Informasi dan keterangan lebih lanjut dapat menghubungi:</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">CONTACT CENTER BANK INDONESIA 131</span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Roboto, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">PERINGATAN! Hati-hati terhadap penipuan. Bank Indonesia tidak memungut biaya apapun selama proses seleksi.</span>', '2017-04-14', '2017-03-04', '0000-00-00', 1);

-- Table `materi` --
CREATE TABLE `materi` (
  `materiID` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `stafID` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `id_kejuruan` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `judulMateri` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `fileMateri` text NOT NULL,
  `deskripsi` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  `uploaded` date NOT NULL,
  `extension` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `size` varchar(255) NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`materiID`),
  KEY `userID` (`stafID`),
  KEY `id_kejuruan` (`id_kejuruan`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

-- Table `pendidikan` --
CREATE TABLE `pendidikan` (
  `id_pendidikan` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `nama` varchar(64) NOT NULL,
  `keterangan` varchar(255) DEFAULT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_pendidikan`)
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=15 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8;

INSERT INTO `pendidikan` (`id_pendidikan`, `nama`, `keterangan`) VALUES
(11, 'SMP', ''),
(12, 'SMA', ''),
(13, 'STM', ''),
(14, 'SMK', '');

-- Table `peserta` --
CREATE TABLE `peserta` (
  `id_peserta` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT,
  `nama` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `id_kejuruan` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `nik` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `ttl` text NOT NULL,
  `jk` enum('pria','wanita') NOT NULL,
  `id_agama` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `skawin` enum('Menikah','Belum') NOT NULL,
  `id_pendidikan` int(11) NOT NULL,
  `alamat` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `telp` varchar(25) NOT NULL,
  `p_kursus` text,
  `p_kerja` text,
  `nama_ortu` varchar(50) NOT NULL,
  `pk_ortu` varchar(30) NOT NULL,
  `alamat_ortu` varchar(100) NOT NULL,
  `ijazah` varchar(450) NOT NULL,
  `ktp` varchar(450) NOT NULL,
  `tanggalDaftar` date NOT NULL,
  `status_peserta` enum('0','1') NOT NULL,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id_peserta`),
  KEY `id_kejuruan` (`id_kejuruan`),
  KEY `id_agama` (`id_agama`),
  KEY `id_pendidikan` (`id_pendidikan`),
  CONSTRAINT `peserta_ibfk_2` FOREIGN KEY (`id_agama`) REFERENCES `agama` (`id_agama`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE,
  CONSTRAINT `peserta_ibfk_3` FOREIGN KEY (`id_pendidikan`) REFERENCES `pendidikan` (`id_pendidikan`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE,
  CONSTRAINT `peserta_ibfk_4` FOREIGN KEY (`id_kejuruan`) REFERENCES `kejuruan` (`id_kejuruan`) ON DELETE CASCADE ON UPDATE CASCADE
) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=21 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

